{"tid":688895,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全菲律賓警員齊「封槍」提醒警員要克制","createTime":"2018-06-03T15:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:44:09.000Z","uid":20148,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec6d79946cec949bbfd080d9e862573a1ad56ae","tid":688895,"uid":20148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/234251_9469ee668068a5e18da1e33772f15c22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F234251_9469ee668068a5e18da1e33772f15c22.png&h=a9a3da67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/234252_b8d0b60fe5ba1a87d610fdb17b0889e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F234252_b8d0b60fe5ba1a87d610fdb17b0889e1.png&h=8335a7f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/234253_a308107ea595f18537d2ddbf23a9d9bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F234253_a308107ea595f18537d2ddbf23a9d9bd.png&h=e7991733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聖誕及新年假期即將到來，菲律賓各級警察機構周一同步舉行「封槍」儀式，在全國約15萬名警員的配槍槍口貼上膠紙，以向公眾保證，警察不會在節日狂歡時胡亂開槍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓國家警察早前向全國警員下達備忘錄，下令加大力度打擊非法使用槍支及胡亂開槍等行為。警方指，「封槍」儀式向該國所有持槍者，特別是軍人、警察等執法人員，「傳遞強烈信號」，提醒他們在節日狂歡期間，要克制自己不使用槍支，以防造成傷亡。當局也會與軍方及其他執法機構，加強情報搜集，查處違規用槍者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20141222/bknint-20141222163720697-1222_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141222%2Fbknint-20141222163720697-1222_17011_001.html&d=hpq7ZA7EHjIIdPpRstEu%2FL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=7c8573e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20141222/bknint-20141222163720697-1222_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n笑撚死 呢個國家真係豬揼兜<img src=\"/assets/